Title : Esther Frumkin
Text : '''Esther Frumkin''' born '''Khaye Malke Lifshits''' (1880, [[Minsk]] - 1943), published under the [[Mononymous person|mononym]] '''Esther''', {{lang-yi|עסטער}}, was a leader of the Yiddish socialist [[General Jewish Labour Bund in Lithuania, Poland and Russia]], and later of the [[Yevsektsiya]] in the Soviet Union.

